{"tid":709353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北京動物園遊客拿石頭掟老虎 女遊客：拿大點的！","createTime":"2018-06-20T02:37:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T10:28:19.000Z","uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"daff58d078a70a4bbf5222cbd49c7664c5dc3d13","tid":709353,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T02:37:04.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】近日，內地有網民在網上發佈影片稱，在北京大興野生動物園遊玩時，碰到一家遊客不斷拾起地上的石頭擲向籠內的老虎。短片中可見，兩名男子曾數次從地上拾起石頭向籠內老虎投擲，旁邊一名拿着手機拍攝的女子更不時說：「再掟多塊，攞大塊的打牠就會動了。」短片發佈後，擲石遊客不文明的行為遭到一眾網民指責。目前園方正核實遊客拿石擲向老虎一事。<br />\n<br />\n據目擊者稱，自己在北京野生動物園遊玩時遇到上述遊客。拍攝影片後，有工作人員出面制止了對方繼續擲石頭，具體如何處理尚不清楚，「我們也只是過來遊玩的，拍了之後就離開了。走的時候感覺員工在和涉事遊客交涉。」他表示，在野生動物園還遇見了很多令人無語的事情，「有些家長帶孩子喂小動物食物，飼養員勸了好多次，說這些都是珍稀動物，食物都是通過特殊處理的，要是出問題卻又是飼養員的責任，若抓傷小孩子又得動物園賠，但是勸說完那些大人依然厚着臉皮繼續讓孩子去餵，讓孩子和野生動物親密接觸。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%8B%95%E7%89%A9%E5%9C%92%E9%81%8A%E5%AE%A2%E6%8B%BF%E7%9F%B3%E9%A0%AD%E6%8E%9F%E8%80%81%E8%99%8E-%E5%A5%B3%E9%81%8A%E5%AE%A2-%E6%8B%BF%E5%A4%A7%E9%BB%9E%E7%9A%84-030800112.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%2589%25A9%25E5%259C%2592%25E9%2581%258A%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E6%258B%25BF%25E7%259F%25B3%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E6%258E%259F%25E8%2580%2581%25E8%2599%258E-%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E9%2581%258A%25E5%25AE%25A2-%25E6%258B%25BF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%25BB%259E%25E7%259A%2584-030800112.html&d=4p24QOPJguqBpXfAtBOJjCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=e99ae008\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%8B%95%E7%89%A9%E5%9C%92%E9%81%8A%E5%AE%A2%E6%8B%BF%E7%9F%B3%E9%A0%AD%E6%8E%9F%E8%80%81%E8%99%8E-%E5%A5%B3%E9%81%8A%E5%AE%A2-%E6%8B%BF%E5%A4%A7%E9%BB%9E%E7%9A%84-030800112.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"480a4f4acaef08df8b9d75c3dad6038bb3145a6c","tid":709353,"uid":14918,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T02:39:41.000Z","msg":"這是真的假的<br />\n動也不動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69735f9bffecb71fe927b658518c4df36f08a735","tid":709353,"uid":95,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T02:44:49.000Z","msg":"支那人=地球毒瘤"},{"pid":"d76ae56d3c1d82198f971f0e635cf277c7ba4179","tid":709353,"uid":121130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T03:43:27.000Z","msg":"餵動物好呀 <br />\n餵埋d蝗仔最好<br />\n功德無量呀"},{"pid":"cf66387b401df110c86d15e8e0a38ebb6eff4930","tid":709353,"uid":107927,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T03:45:27.000Z","msg":"沒事兒沒事兒"},{"pid":"73de7fca5d432088623f888157e1778c07b9eb91","tid":709353,"uid":44646,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T03:46:29.000Z","msg":"個記者PK到<br />\n<br />\n原片中人講普通話，<br />\n因咩9佢用廣東話寫出說話內容？"},{"pid":"4eadc111b0e8164aa5031183013cf72d3661b826","tid":709353,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T03:47:50.000Z","msg":"支那人係咁架啦"},{"pid":"f996f11441a7bbce0ea10f877161878142e3fa56","tid":709353,"uid":82829,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"73de7fca5d432088623f888157e1778c07b9eb91","tid":709353,"uid":44646,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T03:46:29.000Z","msg":"個記者PK到<br />\n<br />\n原片中人講普通話，<br />\n因咩9佢用廣東話寫出說話內容？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T03:48:53.000Z","msg":"yahoo 奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbfcfd0eeb4eb68c94e6f0b321e3b820d635930d","tid":709353,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"73de7fca5d432088623f888157e1778c07b9eb91","tid":709353,"uid":44646,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T03:46:29.000Z","msg":"個記者PK到<br />\n<br />\n原片中人講普通話，<br />\n因咩9佢用廣東話寫出說話內容？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T03:49:07.000Z","msg":"星島日報<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4b4297c6dce260e0416dd2b6db0a7c92657ff7